@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
actor User
rectangle "React SPA\nBrowser Client" as spa
rectangle "Flask API\nHTTPS + JSON + SSE" as api
database "PostgreSQL\nSystem of Record" as db
queue "Redis + Celery\nQueue and Workers" as queue
cloud "Email Provider" as email

User --> spa : uses
spa --> api : REST + SSE
api --> db : reads / writes
api --> queue : outbox relay
queue --> db : projections / delivery state
queue --> email : transactional mail
@enduml
